reviewText: Enjoyed  this  movie . Not  only  does  it  have  a  great  message  you  will  learn  some  history  too.
Great family adventure! Unique plot-line really keeps you engaged and there is no content here that you have to worry about.
My entire family loved this movie! The plot was clever with great messages about patriotism and faith. There's a lot of action and suspense. It really keeps you engaged!
Good clean fun that kept the kids interested. The kids might even learn a little history as well as some facts about Washington DC.

I really enjoy "detective" type movies. This one was really interesting and had a surprisingly good storyline. I would definitely watch it again. Also enjoyed what they said about how this country is based on God. I would definitely recommend it.
I was surprised by how well made it was. Enjoyable story and characters, and good clean family fun.
Nice teen movie with some history and mystery.
Yet more sappy religious dogma disguised as a movie.
